      &lt;img alt="The green Hulu logo set against a background of shapes colored green, cream, and black." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/rFYQh1Hyqw4-Z40N1w4_70663wg=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73450204/acastro_STK061_hulu_01.0.jpg" /&gt;
