&lt;p lang="en" dir="ltr"&gt;The default iOS 18 wallpaper now has a dynamic option &lt;br&gt;Changing according to time of the day ig &lt;a href="https://t.co/ejCtVVG4lQ"&gt;pic.twitter.com/ejCtVVG4lQ&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;— ShrimpApplePro   ずっと真夜中でいいのに (@VNchocoTaco) &lt;a href="https://twitter.com/VNchocoTaco/status/1810384598926500064?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw"&gt;July 8, 2024&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;


&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p id="Zv5NAO"&gt;The new dynamic wallpaper is just one of a bunch of new customization features &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/10/24172132/apple-ios-18-new-features-ai"&gt;coming to iOS 18&lt;/a&gt;: you'll also be able to tint your homescreen app...&lt;/p&gt;
